Hey all,

I've noticed a problem with my breaks, now that the break booster is hooked
up
again. As I'm driving, very gradually the breaks begin to apply. At first
it's not too noticeable. Then eventually the bus begins to slow down too
much
when I shift (it doesn't coast anymore). Soon the engine becomes noticeably
labored.
